  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collateral Dungeon is a tactical puzzle dungeon crawler. Explore as an archaeologist trapped in your most recent dig: an enemy-infested dungeon. However, you are a lover, not a fighter. Without weapons, you must turn to your wit and clever traps to defeat enemies lest you relive your failings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/87ed2fc211758c36e440a3c2185bec28.poster.avif?t=1745859621\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/87ed2fc211758c36e440a3c2185bec28.webm?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/87ed2fc211758c36e440a3c2185bec28.mp4?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore procedurally generated dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRAP ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/06d55d6e1d9fae53a4fa3e25f4423fa6.poster.avif?t=1745859621\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/06d55d6e1d9fae53a4fa3e25f4423fa6.webm?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/06d55d6e1d9fae53a4fa3e25f4423fa6.mp4?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place traps to ensnare your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REWIND TIME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/563faed7afaabba523ca8f0a52932082.poster.avif?t=1745859621\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/563faed7afaabba523ca8f0a52932082.webm?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/563faed7afaabba523ca8f0a52932082.mp4?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewind time if your enemies find you, or you stumble into your own traps.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Discover Relics<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/fee837b3f3c8550c4ebe6fc6c4c3ce38.poster.avif?t=1745859621\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/fee837b3f3c8550c4ebe6fc6c4c3ce38.webm?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826430/extras/fee837b3f3c8550c4ebe6fc6c4c3ce38.mp4?t=1745859621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover relics from the past, present, and future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally Generated Dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based tactics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grid-based movement </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade mode for endless replayability</p></li></ul>",
